short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Redirects numbers to a custom URL

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Quickly redirects numbers typed on the address bar to a custom URL after hitting enter.
Setup is simple and easy!

Example profile settings:
https://agile-jira.pension.com/browse/BRWNT-{x}
https://group-one.atlassian.net/browse/WEBSHOP-{x}

If your team is using the JIRA as a git branch or part of the commit message
https://gitlab.com/search?search=BRWNT-{x}

If your favourite anime has the episode number in its URL
https://onepiece.fandom.com/wiki/Episode_{x}


Additional features soon!

We don't track or store any data for your privacy.
